SELECT COALESCE("USERID", "USERID") AS "USERID", "DISPLAYNAME", "TOTALPOSTS", "QUESTIONS", "ANSWERS", "TOTALSCORE", "TOTALVIEWS", "BADGECOUNT", "GOLDBADGES", "SILVERBADGES", "BRONZEBADGES"
FROM (SELECT "Users"."Id" AS "USERID", "Users"."DisplayName" AS "DISPLAYNAME", CASE WHEN "t0"."TOTALPOSTS" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t0"."TOTALPOSTS" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "TOTALPOSTS", CASE WHEN "t0"."QUESTIONS" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t0"."QUESTIONS" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "QUESTIONS", CASE WHEN "t0"."ANSWERS" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t0"."ANSWERS" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "ANSWERS", CASE WHEN "t0"."TOTALSCORE" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t0"."TOTALSCORE" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "TOTALSCORE", CASE WHEN "t0"."TOTALVIEWS" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t0"."TOTALVIEWS" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "TOTALVIEWS", CASE WHEN "t3"."BADGECOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."BADGECOUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "BADGECOUNT", CASE WHEN "t3"."GOLDBADGES" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."GOLDBADGES" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "GOLDBADGES", CASE WHEN "t3"."SILVERBADGES" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."SILVERBADGES" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "SILVERBADGES", CASE WHEN "t3"."BRONZEBADGES" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."BRONZEBADGES" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "BRONZEBADGES"
FROM "STACK"."Users"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "OwnerUserId" AS "OWNERUSERID", COUNT(*) AS "TOTALPOSTS", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("PostTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "QUESTIONS", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("PostTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "ANSWERS", SUM("Score") AS "TOTALSCORE", SUM("ViewCount") AS "TOTALVIEWS"
FROM "STACK"."Posts"
GROUP BY "OwnerUserId") AS "t0" ON "Users"."Id" = "t0"."OWNERUSERID"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT ANY_VALUE("Users0"."Id") AS "USERID", "Users0"."DisplayName" AS "DISPLAYNAME", COUNT("Badges"."Id") AS "BADGECOUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Badges"."Class" AS INTEGER) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "GOLDBADGES", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Badges"."Class" AS INTEGER) = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "SILVERBADGES", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Badges"."Class" AS INTEGER) = 3 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "BRONZEBADGES"
FROM "STACK"."Users" AS "Users0"
LEFT JOIN "STACK"."Badges" ON "Users0"."Id" = "Badges"."UserId"
GROUP BY "Users0"."Id", "Users0"."DisplayName") AS "t3" ON "Users"."Id" = "t3"."USERID") AS "t4"
WHERE "t4"."TOTALPOSTS" > 0